data.description: POOL HOME! No HOA, No CDD. In an established neighborhood.  Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a formal living room, a formal dining room, a family room, an inside laundry room, wood floors, bonus space, tons of natural light, concrete block, updated plumbing and electrical. Screened in-ground pool perfect for entertaining guests! Conveniently located near schools, shopping, restaurants, hospitals, and Downtown Jacksonville. Schedule your showing today! Property Sold AS IS.
